BASE - Click general element
Project ID of project name [JITDatabase016a]
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitparent" and Comment "Table jitparent"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitparent" display
When I add new table with Name "jitchilde2e" and Comment "Testing jitchilde2e"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitchilde2e" display
When I drag the table Name "jitchilde2e" to new location with x: "500", y: "0"
When I trigger relation popup established from table Name "jitparent" to table Name "jitchilde2e"
When I check radio button popup Name "has one"
Then I should NOT see checkbox popup Name "Counter cache" displayed
When I check radio button popup Name "has many"
When I check checkbox popup Name "Counter cache"
When I update popup with textbox Name "Cache column" to value "jitera"
When I press Save button modal popup
Then I should see the realtion path display
Then I should see column with name "jitera" and index "4" of table name "jitparent" has type "counter_cache" display
Then I should see column with name "jitchilde2es" and index "5" of table name "jitparent" has type "Model" display
Then I should see column with name "jitparent_id" and index "4" of table name "jitchilde2e" has type "foreign_key" display
When I open relation popup of pair "jitparent-jitchilde2e"
Then I should see dropdown popup Name "Target" has value "jitchilde2es"
Then I should see checkbox popup Name "Counter cache" is checked
Then I should see textbox popup Name "Cache column" has value "jitera"
When I update popup with textbox Name "Cache column" to value "jiteraupdate"
When I press Save button modal popup
Then I should see column with name "jiteraupdate" and index "4" of table name "jitparent" has type "counter_cache" display
When I open popup to see column infos Name "jiteraupdate" of table with Name "jitparent"
Then I should see textbox popup Name "Column name" has value "jiteraupdate"
Then I should see dropdown popup Name "Children Table" has value "jitchilde2es"
When I close the modal popup
When I add new column with Name "jiteraothercache" Type "counter_cache" for Table name "jitparent"
When I update popup with dropdown Name "Children Table" to value "jitchilde2es" by clicking
When I press Add column button popup without wait
Then I should see the warning popup with message "Validation failed: Name has already been taken"
When I close the modal popup
When I delete relation path of pair "jitparent-jitchilde2e"
